Package org.hibernate.query.spi

Interface QueryOptions

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MutableQueryOptions
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DelegatingQueryOptions, LoaderSqlAstCreationState, QueryOptionsAdapter, QueryOptionsImpl, QuerySqmImpl.UniqueSemanticFilterQueryOption, SimpleQueryOptions, SqlOmittingQueryOptions
    public interface QueryOptions
    Encapsulates options for the execution of a HQL/Criteria/native query
